episodes.title: Long, Long Way from Home
episodes.plot: Daniel's new ally-turned-housemate tests Amanda's patience. Miguel searches for his father in Mexico. Terry starts to transform Cobra Kai.

episodes.title: Molé
episodes.plot: Chozen and Daniel hatch a risky plot against Terry. In Mexico, Robby and Johnny look for Miguel, who discovers the truth about his dad.

episodes.title: Playing with Fire
episodes.plot: Another enemy from Daniel's past resurfaces. After a spa day and some soul-searching, Sam comes to a decision about her future with Miguel.

episodes.title: Downward Spiral
episodes.plot: Johnny and Carmen's romance flies high while Daniel and Amanda are rattled by Terry's schemes. The teens' feuds spill over at the waterpark.

episodes.title: Extreme Measures
episodes.plot: Daniel leans on a friend - and frenemy. Tensions come to a head for Miguel and Robby. A familiar face returns.

episodes.title: Ouroboros
episodes.plot: Terry recruits an expert in the way of the fist. Daniel walks away from a fight, and Johnny and Chozen pick one. In prison, Kreese confronts old demons.

episodes.title: Bad Eggs
episodes.plot: Terry and Kim issue a brutal challenge while Chozen teaches his students a different kind of lesson. Johnny and Daniel demand answers from Kreese.

episodes.title: Taikai
episodes.plot: A coveted spot in an elite international tournament ignites a fight between dojos. Tory's loyalties are tested. Sam struggles to let Miguel go.

episodes.title: Survivors
episodes.plot: Tory pays a price for defiance. Stingray does battle with his conscience. A celebratory night on the town takes a turn for Johnny, Daniel and Chozen.

episodes.title: Head of the Snake
episodes.plot: A fight night erupts in the Valley as Johnny, Daniel, Chozen and their students summon all their skills and strength to expose Terry and take him down.
